<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4671493>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Aulodrilus limnobius Bretscher from Japan. A, ventral chaeta in V; B, dorsal chaeta in a mid-segment, dorso-lateral view; C, the same, lateral view; D, SEM photomicrograph of dorsal chaetae in a mid-segment; E, lateral view of anterior segments, showing vascular system; F, parasagittal section of genital segments. A–D from Lake Okotanpe, Chitose, Hokkaido Prefecture, Japan; E from Tajiri, Osaki, Miyagi Prefecture, Japan; F from Ozegahara mire, Gunma Prefecture, Japan." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4671493/files/figure.png" .

